    IVisitor<Field>

    public final class PropertyClassFieldVisitorImpl
extends AbstractFieldVisitorImpl
    The final class PropertyClassFieldVisitorImpl models a concrete implementation of the IVisitor interface that is responsible for visiting fields of custom type where the classes have been annotated using the PropertyClass annotation.Array.
